    <string name="c_release_notes_for_title">"Release notes for version "</string>
    <string name="cpp_release_notes_143">★ App language can be changed in settings\n★ Floating
        calculator themes\n★ Widget themes\n★ Various bugfixes, stability and usability improvements</string>
    <string name="cpp_release_notes_148">★ New graph plotter\n★ Improved user interface: main and
        additional screens, dialogs, menus, etc\n★ Redesigned unit converter\n★ Memory button (MC,
        M+, M)\n★ Floating calculator for Android M\n★ Auto-save of recent history\n★ Faster
        start-ups, less memory consumption</string>
    <string name="cpp_release_notes_150">★ Copy/paste buttons\n★ AMOLED theme\n★ Fixed formatting of
        small numbers\n★ Faster graph plotter\n★ Numeral base conversion\n★ E button in Variables
        Editor</string>
    <string name="cpp_release_notes_152">★ High contrast text option\n★ Redesigned settings\n★ More
        number format options: scientific and engineering notations\n★ Small UI tweaks\n★ Bugs fixes</string>
